{"tid":2056582,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"環球專上書院係呃人，同傳銷無分別","createTime":"2020-06-08T19:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T00:24:24.000Z","uid":315470,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"666489e62c59db01305756831377362a10b0c60e","tid":2056582,"uid":315470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T19:39:20.000Z","msg":"有無受害者"},{"pid":"a7e9d4007f7cd2431a73d3883fe078eda33ded13","tid":2056582,"uid":315470,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T19:41:20.000Z","msg":"宜家情況應該不嚴重，但是遲d放榜就會有好多學生比人水左去讀幾萬蚊的垃圾課程，希望推到班傳銷狗吃屎，開唔到飯"},{"pid":"32b9d449cc0a98cad53ab7189168743f0fc9046d","tid":2056582,"uid":316009,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T02:39:33.000Z","msg":"識人係個到讀，讀到傻左咁"},{"pid":"b4c44497b857ba6eb56e2c69c5bfac7964ef2664","tid":2056582,"uid":315470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32b9d449cc0a98cad53ab7189168743f0fc9046d","tid":2056582,"uid":316009,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T02:39:33.000Z","msg":"識人係個到讀，讀到傻左咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:58:42.000Z","msg":"分享下"},{"pid":"aa1d09d79142cf74f9e97284cb88849b75348e95","tid":2056582,"uid":316009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4c44497b857ba6eb56e2c69c5bfac7964ef2664","tid":2056582,"uid":315470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32b9d449cc0a98cad53ab7189168743f0fc9046d","tid":2056582,"uid":316009,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T02:39:33.000Z","msg":"識人係個到讀，讀到傻左咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:58:42.000Z","msg":"分享下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T08:56:54.000Z","msg":"有個朋友俾hkue昆左，求幫手<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1974677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1974677</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c2836954c36cfc7498b05f7c83bf807d97948fd1","tid":2056582,"uid":209650,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T16:12:18.000Z","msg":"名都未聽過"},{"pid":"e9b2e10ddf0f1aca499602d94dbddcde8b895bcd","tid":2056582,"uid":7828,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T16:25:49.000Z","msg":"樓主 pin this<br />\n<br />\n各位DSE學生報讀任何課程前，請先查詢有關課程是否有<span style=\"color: green;\">HKQF（香港資歷架構）</span>的認可，切勿因為一時大意誤信他人被騙。<br />\n<br />\n資歷名冊官網<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Findex.html&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19m58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=fa9ca304\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n資歷搜尋<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Fsearch%2Fqr-search%2F&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19m58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=099e6587\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/</a><br />\n<br />\n基本上傳銷或者詐騙的人，他們喜歡先入為主，不停感情勒索，裝作大家感情深厚<br />\n<br />\n帶你去見工：<br />\n「要為屋企人著想，賺多啲錢」<br />\n「讀大學冇用㗎，呢份工先有錢途」<br />\n「有錢途再追逐自己夢想都唔遲」<br />\n「好自私，只顧及讀書，真係好好好自私，錢又媽比，家境又5好，明知讀完得萬幾蚊，照顧5到屋企，你又讀得5勁，點解要讀？」<br />\n「問你要揀買樓定讀大學，又問你憑咩講話冇時間讀書（因為平時有出黎發夢）<br />\n<br />\n帶你去傳銷學校 ：<br />\n「我想你改變自己」<br />\n「唔好輕易放棄，放棄自己將來」<br />\n「ive/副學士/hd 冇用㗎」<br />\n「想識d有上進心嘅男仔」<br />\n「d顧問好嚴格，記得帶齊所有身份證明文件/證書」<br />\n「張證書有poly 認可㗎，你讀其他之後出嚟做嘢冇用點算」<br />\n（poly 你老母，打過去poly 話唔撚係，只係出席活動的證書，唔會有咩學歷證明，食屎啦臭雞)<br />\n<br />\n帶你去美容：<br />\n「我帶你去做facial呀/你陪我去做facial呀」<br />\n「我當你是朋友才給你這優惠」<br />\n<br />\n[轉貼］<br />\n<br />\n透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[搵工要小心，切勿中美容教育傳銷陷阱]  大學生小心職場陷阱<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164225/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7164225%2Fpage%2F1&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19m58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=03d93fc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164225/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[大學生小心職場陷阱] 小心有傳銷公司成員係交友app 扮係你朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7164242%2Fpage%2F1&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19m58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=00cca9bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n叫你去interview個個聲稱人工係每單Job計 每單job有4位數字，Interview個個就話係計人頭 教育同醫美都唔同計法，前後矛盾<br />\n<br />\n教育分 1-5 6-30 31-465 （重有再上<br />\n1-5:$1000/1<br />\n6-30:$1800/1<br />\n31-465:$2400/1<br />\n<br />\n醫美就計%<br />\n<br />\n佢地聲稱自己唔會由個客手上拎錢<br />\n係客比錢pr公司搵到嘅合作機構<br />\n再由合作機構比返佣pr即係佢地<br />\n<br />\n中匯商業大廈18-20樓<br />\n19樓主要做interview / training，18/20樓好似係office<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/02/15/hcjw3E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F02%2F15%2Fhcjw3E.png&h=fba48af3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee92615bf8570ae4b06f7319ae0436d7c0fa78fd","tid":2056582,"uid":37240,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T16:28:11.000Z","msg":"呢D唔知乜鳩，聽都未聽過既濕鳩假學院都肯比錢讀<br />\n不如留返D錢去驗腦好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad054cc6536f720850e622c5d8e2f825accdae4","tid":2056582,"uid":71279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T16:29:06.000Z","msg":"Hkue, 定uche?"},{"pid":"a2b9f0407387750f52453f88f93baa30f1619922","tid":2056582,"uid":43178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ad054cc6536f720850e622c5d8e2f825accdae4","tid":2056582,"uid":71279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T16:29:06.000Z","msg":"Hkue, 定uche?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T16:36:59.000Z","msg":"一撚樣啦"},{"pid":"83e6f515cb1d98ae6f3311013c81327a74a92350","tid":2056582,"uid":315470,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"2ad054cc6536f720850e622c5d8e2f825accdae4","tid":2056582,"uid":71279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T1