，明知讀完得萬幾蚊，照顧5到屋企，你又讀得5勁，點解要讀？」<br />\n「問你要揀買樓定讀大學，又問你憑咩講話冇時間讀書（因為平時有出黎發夢）<br />\n<br />\n帶你去傳銷學校 ：<br />\n「我想你改變自己」<br />\n「唔好輕易放棄，放棄自己將來」<br />\n「ive/副學士/hd 冇用㗎」<br />\n「想識d有上進心嘅男仔」<br />\n「d顧問好嚴格，記得帶齊所有身份證明文件/證書」<br />\n「張證書有poly 認可㗎，你讀其他之後出嚟做嘢冇用點算」<br />\n（poly 你老母，打過去poly 話唔撚係，只係出席活動的證書，唔會有咩學歷證明，食屎啦臭雞)<br />\n<br />\n帶你去美容：<br />\n「我帶你去做facial呀/你陪我去做facial呀」<br />\n「我當你是朋友才給你這優惠」<br />\n<br />\n[轉貼］<br />\n<br />\n透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[搵工要小心，切勿中美容教育傳銷陷阱]  大學生小心職場陷阱<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164225/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7164225%2Fpage%2F1&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19m58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=03d93fc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164225/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[大學生小心職場陷阱] 小心有傳銷公司成員係交友app 扮係你朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7164242%2Fpage%2F1&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19m58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=00cca9bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n叫你去interview個個聲稱人工係每單Job計 每單job有4位數字，Interview個個就話係計人頭 教育同醫美都唔同計法，前後矛盾<br />\n<br />\n教育分 1-5 6-30 31-465 （重有再上<br />\n1-5:$1000/1<br />\n6-30:$1800/1<br />\n31-465:$2400/1<br />\n<br />\n醫美就計%<br />\n<br />\n佢地聲稱自己唔會由個客手上拎錢<br />\n係客比錢pr公司搵到嘅合作機構<br />\n再由合作機構比返佣pr即係佢地<br />\n<br />\n中匯商業大廈18-20樓<br />\n19樓主要做interview / training，18/20樓好似係office<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/02/15/hcjw3E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F02%2F15%2Fhcjw3E.png&h=fba48af3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:05:37.000Z","msg":"分享下其中一個係入面做嘅大陸騙徒先，有人想要其他我先再Post 埋其他騙徙<br />\n<br />\n騙徒Crystal Li李婉瑩新電話號碼: 91570141<br />\n<br />\n呢個騙徒係大陸人，由汕尾移民落黎香港，專呃d DSE 學生去報冇資歷級別 (HKQF) 嘅課程，另外會呃女性去美容院 <br />\n<br />\n更多資訊： <br />\n<a href=\"https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=62kedb7g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstories.hkjunkcall.com%2F%3Fd%3D62kedb7g&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19m58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=f578e1b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=62kedb7g</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=i4waqbjt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstories.hkjunkcall.com%2F%3Fd%3Di4waqbjt&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19m58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=c6e465c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=i4waqbjt</a> <br />\n<br />\n除咗美容，仲有SELL 教育，中醫，脫毛，投資等等<br />\n<br />\nChampion Team 另一成員 <br />\n如果去見工會見到佢 <br />\n(與Sam Chau Wing Sum 周詠森，Hugo Wong 及 三金合作） <br />\n<br />\n行業：教育及美容傳銷 <br />\n花名：Crystal Li / 水晶梨 <br />\n中文全名：李婉瑩 <br />\n英文全名：Li Wan Ying <br />\n常用工作電話：91570141（Updated) <br />\n另一工作電話：51610763 (可以 iMessage) <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f44ohbs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff44ohbs.jpg&h=a018e3ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1VbXiY9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1VbXiY9.jpg&h=a59da781&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ModKJqQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FModKJqQ.jpg&h=a38f4662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下係佢部分冇p圖嘅真樣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yOkHOCZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyOkHOCZ.jpg&h=f279000e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3mSK1X0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3mSK1X0.jpg&h=be2c20d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"704288fcfedd85476097b38f99464e1c93ad6679","tid":2056582,"uid":240342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T15:16:06.000Z","msg":"有冇人識點扮dse考生<br />\n<br />\n想扮俾人呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":